Notes: 								
1	This certificate has been issued on the basis of verification of unaudited books of accounts of the project upto 15.06.2022.				
2	The promoters have not opened the separate bank account for RERA purpose till 30.06.2021 and have deposited the payment received from customers in the regular bank accounts. In view of this entire amount received from customers have been shown as amount withdrawn till the date. As a result, the  opening and closing balance as per bank will not tally with the bank statements.				
3	The promoters have opened separate RERA bank account in July-2021 but not deposited amount received from allottees in RERA bank account.				
4	The estimated cost of project as per column no A of 1(ii)(a)(i) has been taken on the basis of a certificate of Engineers M/s Kinal D Soni, Ahmedabad and relied upon by us.				
5	The estimated cost of project as per column no A of 1(ii)(a)(iii), (b) and   has been taken on the basis of estimates made by the management.				
6	As on 15.06.2022, unsecured loan as per books of accounts were Rs. 3584.10  lakhs and loan and advances were 892.54 lakhs. As a result, actual utilisation of unsecured loans towards the project was Rs.2691.56 lakhs only. It was not possible for us to identify and verify as to out of total unsecured loan, which unsecured loan was utilised for project and which unsecured loan was given as loans and advance and therefore, we have considered following parties as unsecured loans for project :
